    "elements": [
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "I have smitten you with blasting - Literally, \"an exceeding scorching,\" such as the hot east wind produced, and \"an exceeding mildew,\" a blight, in which the ears turn untimely a pale yellow, and have no grain. Both words are doubly intensive. They stand together in the prophecy of Moses ",
        "children": []
